'''北弗吉尼亚大学'''（{{lang-en|University of Northern Virginia}}，又称“北维大学”）是[[美國|美國]][[弗吉尼亚州|弗吉尼亚州]][[費爾法克斯縣_(維吉尼亞州)|費爾法克斯縣]]{{link-en|安嫩代尔 (弗吉尼亚州)|Annandale, Virginia|安嫩代爾}}的一所營利學校
。这所大学建立于1998年，提供學士、硕士和博士学位。虽然北维大学在美国并不知名，但它自称是最受印度学生欢迎的美国大学。

北维大学受到联邦政府的监视，其学术上和学生签证上的诸多问题也被媒体报道。美国移民海关总署于2011年7月28日突袭了学校办公室，并通知校方政府将取缔学校向国际学生颁发录取通知书的权利。<ref name=ICE>{{cite web|url=http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/43935088 |title=ICE Raids University of Northern Virginia Offices |publisher=MSNBC |date=2011-07-28 |accessdate=2011-07-29}}</ref>印度国会议员[[Kapil_Sibal|Kapil Sibal]]，将北维大学与名声狼藉的“sham university”相比较，并说大学没有任何可接受的认证。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.rediff.com/news/slide-show/slide-show-1-india-has-enough-safeguards-to-keep-away-sham-us-colleges-sibal/20111012.htm |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2013-03-24 |archive-date=2013-11-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131101023204/http://www.rediff.com/news/slide-show/slide-show-1-india-has-enough-safeguards-to-keep-away-sham-us-colleges-sibal/20111012.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref> 虽然印度媒体预测北维大学将于2011年被永久关闭，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.unva.edu/forms/Message_Chancellor.pdf |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-12-19 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120427095803/http://www.unva.edu/forms/Message_Chancellor.pdf |archivedate=2012-04-27 }}</ref> 但学校在那之后仍继续营业。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.unva.edu/forms/message_counsel.pdf |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-12-19 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120427095829/http://www.unva.edu/forms/message_counsel.pdf |archivedate=2012-04-27 }}</ref>

2013年7月16日，弗吉尼亚州高等教育部取缔了北维大学的运营执照，并强迫学校关闭。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://watchdog.org/95968/university-of-northern-virginia-forced-to-close-leaving-students-in-limbo/ |title=University of Northern Virginia forced to close, leaving students in limbo |author=Bre Payton |date=2013-07-17 |work=Watchdog.org Virginia Bureau |publisher=Franklin Center for Government & Public Integrity |accessdate=2013-09-03 |archive-date=2013-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131031170604/http://watchdog.org/95968/university-of-northern-virginia-forced-to-close-leaving-students-in-limbo/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.schev.edu/schev/AgendaBooks/2013July/Agendabook0713.pdf |title=Agenda Book, July 15-16, 2013 |publisher=State Council of Higher Education for Virginia |page=A-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130813124228/http://www.schev.edu/schev/AgendaBooks/2013July/Agendabook0713.pdf |archivedate=2013-08-13 |accessdate=2013-09-03 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://watchdog.org/96528/soon-to-be-shuttered-va-university-had-history-of-accreditation-problems/|title=Soon-to-be shuttered VA university had history of accreditation problems|author=Bre Payton, Carten Cordell|date=2013-07-19|work=Watchdog.org Virginia Bureau|publisher=Franklin Center for Government & Public Integrity|accessdate=2013-09-03|archive-date=2013-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131031171901/http://watchdog.org/96528/soon-to-be-shuttered-va-university-had-history-of-accreditation-problems/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.schev.edu/students/UNVANotice.pdf|title=Notice Regarding Revocation of University of Northern Virginia|author=State Council of Higher Education for Virginia|date=2013-07-19|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130822221303/http://www.schev.edu/students/UNVANotice.pdf|archivedate=2013-08-22|accessdate=2013-09-03}}</ref>

在2013年10月7日， UNVA对外发布了新的教学地址，在[[南达科他州|南达科他州]]的[[苏瀑|苏瀑]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Northern_Virginia |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2013-10-30 |archive-date=2013-10-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131023151036/http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Northern_Virginia |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 学校创立和运营 ==
北维大学的创立人和主要拥有者是何复国（Daniel Ho), 企业家， 拥有顶好国际超市（Super Q Mart International Food）, 在华盛顿地区有三家分店。北维大学曾经的校长是David V. Lee。他在2011年8月9日辞职，理由是“不想因关于我私人生活的讨论影响北维大学的学生和朋友。”Lee的辞职发生在一篇揭露他性虐待行为的名为“The Smoking Gun”的报告之后。<ref>Jeane MacIntosh, [http://www.nypost.com/p/news/local/sex_tracurricular_college_boss_E3R91btxKbSn7Cd7QTRtBJ Sex-tracurricular college boss] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nypost.com/p/news/local/sex_tracurricular_college_boss_E3R91btxKbSn7Cd7QTRtBJ |date=20120720213713 }}, ''[[New_York_Post|New York Post]]'', August 2, 2011</ref><ref>Rachel Quigley, [http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2021317/UNVA-chancellor-David-Lee-64-sadomasochistic-suburban-sex-dungeon-master.html University chancellor, 64, exposed as sadomasochistic, suburban sex-dungeon master] {{Wayback|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2021317/UNVA-chancellor-David-Lee-64-sadomasochistic-suburban-sex-dungeon-master.html |date=20140118190402 }}, Daily Mail Online, August 20, 2011</ref> Habib Khan 成为继任校长。<ref name=resignation>[http://www.unva.edu/forms/change_chancellor.pdf Lee Resignation letter] {{Wayback|url=http://www.unva.edu/forms/change_chancellor.pdf |date=20110928192811 }}, August 19, 2011, UNVA official website (accessed August 19, 2011)</ref> 2012年8月9日, Habib Khan辞职. 新任校长为北维大学前教育部主任Ali Dastmalchi（中译名为：阿里.达士马驰）.<ref>[http://www.unva.edu/message-chancellor.html Message from Chancellor] {{Wayback|url=http://www.unva.edu/message-chancellor.html |date=20130326013953 }} UNVA official website (accessed September 3, 2012)</ref>

